{
  "id": "prologue",
  "title": "宇宙への旅立ち",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "scene_1_earth_departure",
      "type": "cutscene",
      "background": "earth_spaceport",
      "music": "departure_theme",
      "characters": [],
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "text": "西暦2157年、地球。",
          "effect": "fade_in"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "text": "人類は宇宙の様々な星と交流を始めていた。",
          "effect": "stars_twinkle"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "text": "しかし、言語の壁が大きな問題となっていた。",
          "effect": "language_symbols_float"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "text": "そんな中、伝説の装置「Universal Translator」が突然機能を停止した。",
          "effect": "glitch_effect"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "text": "宇宙の平和を守るため、若き探検家が旅立つ時が来た。",
          "effect": "dramatic_pause"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_2_player_introduction",
      "type": "interactive",
      "background": "spaceship_interior",
      "music": "preparation_theme",
      "characters": [],
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "system",
          "text": "まずは、あなたの名前を教えてください。",
          "input": {
            "type": "text",
            "variable": "player_name",
            "placeholder": "名前を入力...",
            "validation": {
              "minLength": 1,
              "maxLength": 20
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_3_aura_awakening",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "background": "spaceship_interior",
      "music": "aura_theme",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "aura",
          "position": "center",
          "emotion": "normal",
          "animation": "materialize"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "system",
          "text": "宇宙船のシステムが起動し、ホログラムが現れた。",
          "effect": "hologram_activate"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "システム起動完了。こんにちは、{player_name}さん。",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "私は学習支援AI、AURA（オーラ）です。あなたの宇宙の旅をサポートします。",
          "emotion": "normal"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_1",
          "text": "よろしく、AURA！一緒に頑張ろう！",
          "consequence": {
            "affinity": {
              "aura": 5
            },
            "next": "scene_4_mission_briefing"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_2",
          "text": "AIか...本当に大丈夫かな？",
          "consequence": {
            "affinity": {
              "aura": -2
            },
            "next": "scene_3a_aura_reassurance"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_3",
          "text": "Universal Translatorについて教えて！",
          "consequence": {
            "affinity": {
              "aura": 3
            },
            "next": "scene_3b_translator_explanation"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_3a_aura_reassurance",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "background": "spaceship_interior",
      "music": "aura_theme",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "aura",
          "position": "center",
          "emotion": "determined"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "心配しないでください。私は最新の学習AIです。",
          "emotion": "determined"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "あなたの成長を分析し、最適なサポートを提供します。",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "一緒に頑張りましょう！",
          "emotion": "excited"
        }
      ],
      "next": "scene_4_mission_briefing"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_3b_translator_explanation",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "background": "spaceship_interior",
      "music": "mystery_theme",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "aura",
          "position": "center",
          "emotion": "normal"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "Universal Translatorは、全宇宙の言語を瞬時に翻訳する伝説の装置です。",
          "emotion": "normal",
          "effect": "hologram_display"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "しかし、3日前に突然機能が停止しました。",
          "emotion": "worried"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "原因は不明ですが、Language Galaxyの各惑星で異常が発生しているようです。",
          "emotion": "confused"
        }
      ],
      "next": "scene_4_mission_briefing"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_4_mission_briefing",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "background": "spaceship_interior",
      "music": "mission_theme",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "aura",
          "position": "center",
          "emotion": "normal"
        },
        {
          "id": "captain_nova",
          "position": "right",
          "emotion": "determined",
          "animation": "slide-in-right"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "captain_nova",
          "text": "みんな、聞いてくれ！",
          "emotion": "determined"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "captain_nova",
          "text": "私はCaptain Nova。この任務のリーダーだ。",
          "emotion": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "captain_nova",
          "text": "{player_name}、君の力が必要だ。Language Galaxyを救おう！",
          "emotion": "excited"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "ミッションデータを表示します。",
          "emotion": "normal",
          "effect": "data_display"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "第一目標：Sound Planetで音の結晶を修復する。",
          "emotion": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "第二目標：Word Planetで失われた言葉を取り戻す。",
          "emotion": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "第三目標：Grammar Planetで文法エンジンを再起動する。",
          "emotion": "normal"
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "choice_4",
          "text": "分かった！すぐに出発しよう！",
          "consequence": {
            "affinity": {
              "captain_nova": 5,
              "aura": 3
            },
            "next": "scene_5_departure"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_5",
          "text": "でも、どうして私が選ばれたの？",
          "consequence": {
            "affinity": {
              "captain_nova": 2
            },
            "next": "scene_4a_chosen_one"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "choice_6",
          "text": "準備はできてる？危険はないの？",
          "consequence": {
            "affinity": {
              "aura": 2
            },
            "next": "scene_4b_safety_briefing"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_4a_chosen_one",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "background": "spaceship_interior",
      "music": "emotional_theme",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "captain_nova",
          "position": "right",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "id": "aura",
          "position": "center",
          "emotion": "normal"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "captain_nova",
          "text": "君には特別な才能がある。言語を学ぶ情熱と勇気だ。",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "データ分析によると、{player_name}さんの学習適応能力は非常に高いです。",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "captain_nova",
          "text": "信じてくれ。君なら必ずできる！",
          "emotion": "determined"
        }
      ],
      "next": "scene_5_departure"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_4b_safety_briefing",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "background": "spaceship_interior",
      "music": "preparation_theme",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "aura",
          "position": "center",
          "emotion": "normal"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "安全対策は万全です。私が常にサポートします。",
          "emotion": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "各惑星には友好的な住民がいます。彼らが助けてくれるでしょう。",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "学習を通じて、あなたは強くなります。心配いりません。",
          "emotion": "determined"
        }
      ],
      "next": "scene_5_departure"
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_5_departure",
      "type": "cutscene",
      "background": "space_departure",
      "music": "epic_departure",
      "characters": [
        {
          "id": "captain_nova",
          "position": "left",
          "emotion": "determined"
        },
        {
          "id": "aura",
          "position": "right",
          "emotion": "excited"
        }
      ],
      "dialogue": [
        {
          "speaker": "captain_nova",
          "text": "エンジン始動！Language Galaxyへ向けて出発だ！",
          "emotion": "excited",
          "effect": "engine_start"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "aura",
          "text": "ワープドライブ、充電完了。座標をSound Planetに設定。",
          "emotion": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "captain_nova",
          "text": "{player_name}、準備はいいか？",
          "emotion": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "text": "宇宙船は地球を離れ、星々の海へと飛び立った。",
          "effect": "spaceship_launch"
        },
        {
          "speaker": "narrator",
          "text": "Language Galaxyでの大冒険が、今始まる！",
          "effect": "warp_jump"
        }
      ],
      "next": "chapter1_start"
    }
  ],
